story.text: Kamila leaves today. Sad day. Will miss her. But, headed to NYC shortly for swearing in ceremony and then to Maine for John and Kelsey's wedding.
Eddie stopped by last night to discuss the deck. Thing is taking shape and really starting to feel real. He reaffirmed much of what I thought should happen. Really exciting times.
Tom and Kelly are getting married next week and I need to write a poem for the occasion.
